name: A Journey Through the Unknown
description:
A Journey Through the Unknown

AJTU is a text adventure game entirely generated by AI. You explore an alien world and make choices that will affect the outcome of a story while it unfolds in front of you. Your choices will lead you across any of 819 unique events.

This project is open source under the GPL-3 license, you can find the source code here: https://github.com/au-re/AJTU

This game was made in about a week for the All by AI gamejam https://itch.io/jam/allbyai
